						<h1>Dhamma Service</h1>
						<div class="contentStory" >
							<div class="inlineLeft"><img border="0" src="../Images/KitchenService.small.jpg" alt="KitchenServers" /></div>
							<p ><span class="displayText">Meditation and Dhamma Service</span><br/>are like two wings of a bird or two wheels of a cart. For one to progress in Dhamma, both need to be of the same size and strength. The giving of Dhamma Service, whether in a course or in some other way to help in the spread of Dhamma, is one of the most valuable experiences a student of Vipassana can have.</p>

